1. How do you create an array of strings named courses in an XML file?
Ans: <string-array name="courses"><item>Java</item>...</string-array>

2. After creating an InputStream named stream, how do you return a Bitmap from a method?
Ans: return BitmapFactory.decodeStream(stream);

3. How do you pass data to another activity if you have an Intent named "intent"?
Ans: intent.putExtra()

4. In order to get two activities to coordinate with each other, which method should you use?
Ans: startActivityForResult()
